{"tid":1991774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【衷心感謝】訂閱稍回升 黎智英：將推出贈閱券 望大家支持","createTime":"2020-04-27T16:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T19:39:18.000Z","uid":78546,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ce94c71e60d0b1e8c98586d598e3f6ffaa9c7ca1","tid":1991774,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"自從壹傳媒創辦人黎智英發出告急短片 ，加上新推出的App內月費訂閱計劃 ，《蘋果動新聞》的訂閱人數終於稍有回升至60萬，新增了約3萬位訂戶，黎智英表示衷心感謝！<br />\n<br />\n早前因疫情問題及經濟轉差，訂閱人數曾跌破60萬大關，現終於稍為回升，雖然與收支平衡仍有段距離，黎智英已表示要感激大家支持，同時他亦反映，有不少讀者除了自己訂閱《蘋果》，更希望課金，「作為一門生意，課金是有違我們的原則，所以我們將會推出一個新計劃叫贈閱券（贈閱蘋果計劃），大家可以買贈閱券給親戚朋友，這樣便會幫助提升訂閱人數了。」贈閱蘋果計劃將會在稍後時間公佈詳情，只要網上購買「贈閱券」，即可送給親朋，讓他們可以免費盡覽《蘋果》內容。<br />\n<br />\n不少人支持的同時反映《蘋果》做得不足，尤其是登入問題，以至內容方面都需要改善，黎智英為此衷心致歉，「知道這是我們的責任，會正視問題加以改善，在內容質量方面，現正內部檢討和使用不同措施，希望做得更好，並讓讀者看見成果，從而繼續支持我們！」黎智英表示，在《蘋果》做得不足的情況下，仍然得到廣大市民支持，感到非常感動，由衷感謝！<br />\n<br />\n【立即訂閱：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3dmqG9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3dmqG9c&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4aDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=57c9f9e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3dmqG9c</a> 】<br />\n【贊助學生免費睇蘋果：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PvsUuK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PvsUuK&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4aDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=e371b782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PvsUuK</a> 】<br />\n<br />\n💁🏻&zwj;♀️ APP內1-CLICK 10秒訂閱<br />\n毋須再因輸入信用卡資料感到麻煩！現在壹會員只要在《蘋果》app內按「我要訂閱」，即可訂閱月費計劃。同時，現在iOS用戶都可以透過Facebook或Google登入賬戶，毋須每次輸入密碼，更方便順暢。<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VpoIxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VpoIxM&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4aDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=0bcc9439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VpoIxM</a><br />\n<br />\n🍎 8折全年睇《蘋果》即慳$121！<br />\n現有日費訂戶亦可轉訂：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2RVzYzV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RVzYzV&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4aDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=81c58eed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2RVzYzV</a><br />\n============<br />\n✉️ 顧客服務部電郵：cs@nextdigital.com.hk<br />\n📞 顧客服務部電話：+852 2623-9985<br />\n💬 FB Messenger 特快客服：<a href=\"https://hk.adai.ly/e/fbcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.adai.ly%2Fe%2Ffbcs&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4aDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=1c48398e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.adai.ly/e/fbcs</a><br />\n服務時間：星期一至日 上午9時至下午8時 (香港時間)<br />\n非服務時間的查詢將於翌日回覆"},{"pid":"ca743abced95ca4af753f5b07a5037eb015cf71a","tid":1991774,"uid":124983,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"得60萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e0fc3ee0754f6c54cf0a9271c0ead0ea89a60a","tid":1991774,"uid":92448,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"屌你, 一開頭80萬人, 少左成20萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b773bcd03a81781e1007774ad5380eba8f566159","tid":1991774,"uid":36692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"出黎遊行果 200 萬人去左邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191b240722b65d6aac3a93d50d8ae0fb91998681","tid":1991774,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fa5705a7341dffa0a924bd3a36b6b4489dabeb","tid":1991774,"uid":19004,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"大把人係share 個fd 個account 去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Netflix 都咁啦 咪睇得香港人太高"},{"pid":"61b7af67d87289a436dbffe9e343583d4beb02b6","tid":1991774,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"希望少咗果20萬返出來"},{"pid":"529fe13eed5d0fec7301841ba504ec4f084402ee","ti